RELEASE NOTES ARsun v0.1

App that displays the sun or moons position and past and future track in a virtual reailty overlay

FEATURES

Sun and moon data is collected from the USNO website while connected to internet
Moon data is calculated locally if no connection available
Low pass filter for smoothing motion data has been tweaked
Tracked body stops at screen edge to indicate direction to user
Horizon indicator added, multiple ones can be added at different degrees and line lengths

While the splash screen does support screen rotation, the graphing algorithm for the sun
and moon has not been perfected for landscape mode. The main activity is locked in the
portrait position